      "text": "いえ。昨夜の枕投げを見て、ぴんと来たんです",
      "startTime": 43.5965097226,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-stm003.wav",
      "text": "この五人がいいんだ！　って",
      "startTime": 48,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "枕をぶつけられておいて、よくそんな風に思えますね～",
      "startTime": 50.4386861837,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-kkr002.wav",
      "text": "ある意味、尊敬します～",
      "startTime": 55.012107957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "決め手は……みなさんの「素」の可愛さです！",
      "startTime": 57.3573473249,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
